source.name: LED's OnTheMap Interactive Tool
source.description: The OnTheMap application provides detailed spatial distributions of workers' employment and residential locations and the relation between the two at the Census Block level. OnTheMap also provides characteristic detail on age, earnings, industry distributions, and local workforce indicators.
